{"type":"text","timestamp":1775859192298,"sessionID":"ses_2868bf733ffe4397rY07cpTBSx","part":{"id":"prt_d7974ab21001Ca9EsGVji6aSWO","messageID":"msg_d79747766001rwL6QMLoP4pcDs","sessionID":"ses_2868bf733ffe4397rY07cpTBSx","type":"text","text":"## AR-009 Archive Summary: Router HTTP 反向代理核心\n\n### ✅ Completed\n\n| Item | Status | Details |\n|------|--------|---------|\n| **Delta Specification** | ✅ Complete | 14 requirement categories with detailed Gherkin-style scenarios covering HTTP server, health endpoints, session resolution, reverse proxy, JWT injection, error handling, concurrency limiting, and CLI flags |\n| **Design Document** | ✅ Complete | Full architecture with component diagrams, data structures, API contracts, algorithms (session resolution, URL resolution, JWT generation), error handling strategy, and file structure |\n| **Architecture Design** | ✅ Complete | High-level design with HTTP Server Layer → Gin Router Layer → Handler Layer flow |\n| **API Contracts** | ✅ Defined | Health endpoints (`/health/live`, `/health/ready`) and invocation endpoints for AgentRuntime and CodeInterpreter |\n| **Configuration Spec** | ✅ Defined | Environment variables (`WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL`, `AGENTCUBE_NAMESPACE`) and CLI flags |\n\n---\n\n### ⏸️ Deferred / Not Started\n\n| Item | Status | Reason |\n|------|--------|--------|\n| **Phase 1: Design** | ⏸️ TBD | Plan document only contains placeholders |\n| **Phase 2: Implementation** | ⏸️ TBD | No code written yet |\n| **Phase 3: Testing** | ⏸️ TBD | Test spec has only TBD placeholders |\n| **Phase 4: Integration** | ⏸️ TBD | Not started |\n\n**Open Tasks (from tasks.md):**\n- [ ] Design proxy core architecture\n- [ ] Implement HTTP reverse proxy\n- [ ] Implement route table management\n- [ ] Implement header injection\n- [ ] Implement WebSocket support\n- [ ] Implement connection pooling\n- [ ] Implement timeout and circuit breaker\n- [ ] Implement metrics collection\n- [ ] Implement access logging\n- [ ] Write unit tests\n- [ ] Write integration tests\n\n---\n\n### Summary\n\n**AR-009** is currently in the **design completion stage** with comprehensive specifications finalized. The delta-spec contains 50+ detailed test scenarios, and the design document provides complete architectural guidance. However, **no implementation work has begun** — all coding tasks remain deferred and the plan, tests, and notes documents are empty placeholders.\n\n**Status: Design Complete → Ready for Implementation**","time":{"start":1775859192296,"end":1775859192296}}}
